1
00:01:42,945 --> 00:01:45,105
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:02:24,945 --> 00:02:25,785
What's wrong?

3
00:02:27,705 --> 00:02:29,345
What are you doing, Duan Jiaxu?

4
00:02:29,425 --> 00:02:30,465
What did you call me?

5
00:02:31,225 --> 00:02:33,345
I mean, what did you just do?

6
00:02:33,425 --> 00:02:35,265
Given our current relationship,

7
00:02:35,345 --> 00:02:37,225
you shouldn't be calling me Duan Jiaxu.

8
00:02:37,305 --> 00:02:38,785
You…

9
00:02:38,865 --> 00:02:40,425
I wasn't asleep just now.

10
00:02:40,505 --> 00:02:41,785
I knew what you were doing.

11
00:02:43,705 --> 00:02:45,345
So you weren't asleep, were you?

12
00:02:45,865 --> 00:02:47,265
What did I do just now then?

13
00:02:50,025 --> 00:02:50,905
Tell me.

14
00:02:57,305 --> 00:02:59,425
Come closer. I won't say it out loud.

15
00:03:02,185 --> 00:03:03,345
Closer.

16
00:03:05,065 --> 00:03:06,505
Do you want to whisper it?

17
00:03:15,545 --> 00:03:16,505
I don't know

18
00:03:17,225 --> 00:03:18,625
what I've done either.

19
00:03:24,825 --> 00:03:26,385
That was unexpected.

20
00:03:30,185 --> 00:03:33,425
Even though I did that just now,

21
00:03:33,505 --> 00:03:34,705
it doesn't mean

22
00:03:35,825 --> 00:03:37,745
that I have feelings for you.

23
00:03:37,825 --> 00:03:39,785
Got it? I mean…

24
00:03:39,865 --> 00:03:41,225
I haven't agreed yet.

25
00:03:41,905 --> 00:03:44,265
It doesn't mean you have feelings for me.

26
00:03:45,265 --> 00:03:47,105
That means you took advantage of me.

27
00:03:50,385 --> 00:03:52,905
Well, you took advantage of me first.

28
00:03:54,665 --> 00:03:56,745
Are you saying

29
00:03:57,305 --> 00:03:58,865
that no matter what I do to you,

30
00:03:58,945 --> 00:04:00,145
you will do the same to me?

31
00:04:01,345 --> 00:04:02,625
That's not what I meant.

32
00:04:04,945 --> 00:04:06,465
If you do this again,

33
00:04:06,545 --> 00:04:07,945
I will tell my brother.

34
00:04:08,025 --> 00:04:08,905
Go ahead.

35
00:04:09,545 --> 00:04:10,585
Tell him.

36
00:04:12,425 --> 00:04:13,865
After all,

37
00:04:13,945 --> 00:04:16,184
we'll have to go public sooner or later.

38
00:04:16,265 --> 00:04:17,825
It's better to do it sooner.

39
00:04:26,345 --> 00:04:28,185
I haven't agreed yet.

40
00:04:30,545 --> 00:04:32,185
I've successfully brainwashed you.

41
00:04:35,625 --> 00:04:36,705
Jiaxu…

42
00:04:38,105 --> 00:04:39,345
Stop looking at me.

43
00:04:43,945 --> 00:04:46,465
Jiaxu, you should leave.

44
00:04:46,545 --> 00:04:48,025
I can't focus if you stay here.

45
00:04:49,825 --> 00:04:51,585
Hi, everyone.

46
00:04:52,185 --> 00:04:53,385
-Hello.
-Hello.

47
00:04:53,465 --> 00:04:54,305
I'm an alumnus.

48
00:04:54,385 --> 00:04:55,865
-I'm Wang Lin.
-The speaker is here.

49
00:04:55,945 --> 00:04:58,265
The topic of today's sharing session

50
00:04:58,345 --> 00:04:59,505
is future career planning.

51
00:05:00,465 --> 00:05:01,385
Nice!

52
00:05:05,425 --> 00:05:07,945
I know it seems early to talk about this

53
00:05:08,025 --> 00:05:09,305
since you are only freshmen.

54
00:05:09,385 --> 00:05:12,145
However, I believe in being prepared.

55
00:05:15,425 --> 00:05:16,345
Left.

56
00:05:16,425 --> 00:05:17,865
To the left. That's right.

57
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:21,465
What's wrong?

58
00:05:21,545 --> 00:05:22,425
Yu Xin, look!

59
00:05:22,945 --> 00:05:23,865
What is it?

60
00:05:23,945 --> 00:05:26,185
Sangsang's crush attended her class!

61
00:05:26,265 --> 00:05:27,625
-Look.
-Seriously?

62
00:05:27,705 --> 00:05:28,545
Yes.

63
00:05:30,145 --> 00:05:31,665
They attract so much attention.

64
00:05:32,425 --> 00:05:33,745
-I like it.
-I bet I know why.

65
00:05:33,825 --> 00:05:35,345
He bailed on Sangsang several times,

66
00:05:35,425 --> 00:05:37,345
so he specifically came

67
00:05:37,425 --> 00:05:38,305
to make it up to her!

68
00:05:52,985 --> 00:05:55,225
It feels nice to walk around

69
00:05:55,745 --> 00:05:56,785
on campus.

70
00:05:58,825 --> 00:05:59,785
Didn't you take walks

71
00:05:59,865 --> 00:06:01,265
during your time at university?

72
00:06:01,825 --> 00:06:02,785
I didn't.

73
00:06:03,465 --> 00:06:05,185
Why would I? I had no one to walk with.

74
00:06:05,265 --> 00:06:07,025
Didn't my brother take walks with you?

75
00:06:07,505 --> 00:06:09,225
Your brother taking walks with me?

76
00:06:10,505 --> 00:06:11,905
Am I that desperate?

77
00:06:12,545 --> 00:06:13,665
I'll tell him you said that.

78
00:06:16,065 --> 00:06:17,945
If you enjoy taking walks,

79
00:06:18,505 --> 00:06:20,865
I can keep you company today.

80
00:06:21,425 --> 00:06:23,105
Chen Qiang, go for it!

81
00:06:23,185 --> 00:06:25,025
Chen Qiang, you've got this!

82
00:06:25,105 --> 00:06:27,185
You are the best, Chen Qiang!

83
00:06:27,265 --> 00:06:28,785
-It's Weiwei.
-Chen Qiang, go!

84
00:06:28,865 --> 00:06:29,785
-Want to watch?
-Enough.

85
00:06:29,865 --> 00:06:32,945
-Sure. Let's go.
-Everyone knows he's your boyfriend.

86
00:06:34,465 --> 00:06:35,465
Go for it!

87
00:06:35,545 --> 00:06:37,545
Chen Qiang, go for it!

88
00:06:37,625 --> 00:06:39,225
-You startled me.
-You guys are here too.

89
00:06:39,305 --> 00:06:40,305
-Hi.
-Hi, guys.

90
00:06:40,385 --> 00:06:41,865
-Hello.
-Are you here to watch the game too?

91
00:06:42,545 --> 00:06:44,345
He said he wanted to watch.

92
00:06:44,425 --> 00:06:45,265
Look at Chen Qiang.

93
00:06:50,145 --> 00:06:51,065
Is that your boyfriend?

94
00:06:51,145 --> 00:06:52,025
Yes.

95
00:06:52,545 --> 00:06:53,425
Isn't he cool?

96
00:06:57,865 --> 00:06:59,665
-Are you okay?
-Are you okay?

97
00:06:59,745 --> 00:07:01,545
-Are you okay, Jiang Ming?
-Jiang Ming!

98
00:07:01,625 --> 00:07:02,785
Can you still play?

99
00:07:02,865 --> 00:07:03,985
-Are you okay?
-I'm fine.

100
00:07:04,065 --> 00:07:05,065
I'm okay.

101
00:07:05,145 --> 00:07:06,185
Are you hurt?

102
00:07:06,825 --> 00:07:08,465
-Are you okay?
-Did you sprain your ankle?

103
00:07:09,185 --> 00:07:10,105
Yes.

104
00:07:10,185 --> 00:07:11,625
Elevate your foot.

105
00:07:11,705 --> 00:07:13,225
-Use this iced tea.
-Apply it here.

106
00:07:13,705 --> 00:07:14,665
Thank you.

107
00:07:16,185 --> 00:07:17,465
You should go to the infirmary.

108
00:07:18,025 --> 00:07:18,945
It's okay.

109
00:07:19,025 --> 00:07:19,985
This is an old injury.

110
00:07:20,065 --> 00:07:21,465
I'll be better after resting.

111
00:07:21,545 --> 00:07:23,185
Now we're down one player.

112
00:07:23,265 --> 00:07:24,785
Why don't you guys

113
00:07:24,865 --> 00:07:26,025
find someone to replace me?

114
00:07:28,425 --> 00:07:29,625
Hey.

115
00:07:30,225 --> 00:07:31,305
Can you fill in?

116
00:07:33,505 --> 00:07:34,345
Can I?

117
00:07:36,185 --> 00:07:37,145
Can you play?

118
00:07:39,705 --> 00:07:41,025
Come on. Let's play.

119
00:07:41,105 --> 00:07:41,985
Let's go.

120
00:07:42,665 --> 00:07:43,505
Get some rest.

121
00:07:43,585 --> 00:07:44,625
Hold this for me.

122
00:07:47,385 --> 00:07:48,265
Wait here for me.

123
00:07:49,745 --> 00:07:50,745
You will defend him.

124
00:07:57,185 --> 00:07:58,345
He's pretty good.

125
00:08:01,745 --> 00:08:03,505
Hey! Nice shot!

126
00:08:03,585 --> 00:08:05,865
Sangsang, your crush is pretty good.

127
00:08:05,945 --> 00:08:07,585
That's not just pretty good, okay?

128
00:08:07,665 --> 00:08:09,625
He's perfect.

129
00:08:09,705 --> 00:08:12,025
Sangsang is being pursued
by such a perfect guy.

130
00:08:12,105 --> 00:08:13,225
She's so lucky.

131
00:08:15,505 --> 00:08:17,145
Good job!

132
00:08:17,225 --> 00:08:18,305
Good job!

133
00:08:18,385 --> 00:08:19,665
Nice game!

134
00:08:19,745 --> 00:08:20,705
Shoot!

135
00:08:21,745 --> 00:08:22,585
Come.

136
00:08:23,265 --> 00:08:24,225
Okay.

137
00:08:28,865 --> 00:08:29,825
Yes! Nice job!

138
00:08:29,905 --> 00:08:31,145
He's really good!

139
00:08:31,225 --> 00:08:32,585
-Nice!
-Impressive!

140
00:08:38,985 --> 00:08:40,225
It went in!

141
00:08:51,305 --> 00:08:52,865
He's quite good.

142
00:08:53,905 --> 00:08:55,985
Isn't that guy Sang Zhi's brother?

143
00:08:56,705 --> 00:08:57,985
You misunderstood.

144
00:08:58,065 --> 00:08:59,705
They aren't related.

145
00:09:07,785 --> 00:09:09,865
Have some iced tea after the game.

146
00:09:09,945 --> 00:09:10,785
Thank you.

147
00:09:11,385 --> 00:09:12,705
-Here.
-Do you need a drink?

148
00:09:27,105 --> 00:09:29,385
CHAPTER 17, FALLEN

149
00:09:29,465 --> 00:09:31,425
I WANT US TO BE TOGETHER

150
00:09:34,305 --> 00:09:35,545
Girls.

151
00:09:35,625 --> 00:09:37,585
Do you have any summer plans?

152
00:09:37,665 --> 00:09:39,705
Are you going home or traveling?

153
00:09:41,065 --> 00:09:42,425
I'm not going home for the break.

154
00:09:43,265 --> 00:09:44,385
No?

155
00:09:44,465 --> 00:09:45,585
Where are you going then?

156
00:09:45,665 --> 00:09:47,025
Chen Qiang and I have made plans.

157
00:09:47,105 --> 00:09:48,985
We are going to travel

158
00:09:49,065 --> 00:09:50,505
during the summer break.

159
00:09:50,585 --> 00:09:51,865
Really?

160
00:09:52,425 --> 00:09:53,705
That's so romantic.

161
00:09:53,785 --> 00:09:56,665
-How nice.
-I previously made a game prototype.

162
00:09:56,745 --> 00:09:59,065
A design company has shown interest.

163
00:09:59,145 --> 00:10:00,345
I'm going to intern

164
00:10:00,425 --> 00:10:01,985
at their company this summer.

165
00:10:02,705 --> 00:10:05,025
-Really?
-Congratulations.

166
00:10:06,025 --> 00:10:07,505
Interning during freshman year?

167
00:10:07,585 --> 00:10:08,545
That's right!

168
00:10:09,065 --> 00:10:10,225
It's a great company.

169
00:10:10,305 --> 00:10:12,305
I have to seize the opportunity.

170
00:10:12,385 --> 00:10:14,905
Sangsang, are you going home
for the summer?

171
00:10:15,465 --> 00:10:16,425
I…

172
00:10:17,425 --> 00:10:19,145
Or are you staying here with your crush?

173
00:10:21,825 --> 00:10:23,105
He's too busy.

174
00:10:23,185 --> 00:10:25,065
I don't think he has time for me.

175
00:10:25,945 --> 00:10:28,225
I don't want to go home
for the summer either,

176
00:10:28,305 --> 00:10:31,065
so I want to talk to my mom about it.

177
00:10:31,145 --> 00:10:32,865
I think getting a summer internship

178
00:10:32,945 --> 00:10:34,705
is better than staying at home.

179
00:10:34,785 --> 00:10:36,585
Agreed. Totally agreed.

180
00:10:38,825 --> 00:10:39,665
Yu Xin.

181
00:10:40,185 --> 00:10:41,105
What do I need

182
00:10:41,185 --> 00:10:43,025
to include in my resume?

183
00:10:43,105 --> 00:10:44,145
It's important

184
00:10:44,705 --> 00:10:45,985
to highlight your specialty.

185
00:10:46,545 --> 00:10:47,425
Let me take notes.

186
00:10:48,625 --> 00:10:49,825
And don't forget.

187
00:10:49,905 --> 00:10:51,985
Aren't you good at system maintenance?

188
00:10:52,065 --> 00:10:53,785
Put your system maintenance portfolio on--

189
00:10:53,865 --> 00:10:55,465
-The first page.
-Yes.

190
00:10:55,545 --> 00:10:58,065
-The most visible section.
-Yes. And then…

191
00:11:00,025 --> 00:11:00,865
SANG ZHI

192
00:11:00,945 --> 00:11:01,905
Sang Yan.

193
00:11:09,305 --> 00:11:11,345
What do you want?

194
00:11:11,425 --> 00:11:15,905
SILLY DOG

195
00:11:15,985 --> 00:11:20,105
SILLY DOG

196
00:11:21,385 --> 00:11:23,185
I don't want to go home for the summer.

197
00:11:24,465 --> 00:11:26,865
I plan to get an internship here

198
00:11:26,945 --> 00:11:29,025
to enrich my university life.

199
00:11:29,665 --> 00:11:32,185
I don't want to waste my youth.

200
00:11:32,265 --> 00:11:33,505
While I'm still young,

201
00:11:33,585 --> 00:11:35,465
I want to try everything I can.

202
00:11:35,545 --> 00:11:36,425
So

203
00:11:36,985 --> 00:11:39,785
can you help me talk
to Mom and Dad about this?

204
00:11:41,945 --> 00:11:43,105
If Mom still pressures you

205
00:11:43,185 --> 00:11:45,145
to get married during Chinese New Year,

206
00:11:45,225 --> 00:11:47,065
I'll speak up for you.

207
00:11:49,785 --> 00:11:53,225
SANG ZHI

208
00:12:03,305 --> 00:12:04,625
Let me ask you.

209
00:12:04,705 --> 00:12:06,905
Is your postgraduate boyfriend going home?

210
00:12:08,465 --> 00:12:10,265
Listen, you're coming home for the summer.

211
00:12:11,465 --> 00:12:12,545
Listen to yourself.

212
00:12:12,625 --> 00:12:14,465
I'm embarrassed for you
even through the screen.

213
00:12:27,705 --> 00:12:30,705
SILLY DOG

214
00:12:30,785 --> 00:12:32,385
Don't call me. I'm busy right now.

215
00:12:45,745 --> 00:12:46,665
Sang Yan.

216
00:12:47,225 --> 00:12:49,025
I told you.

217
00:12:49,105 --> 00:12:51,385
I'm staying here for an internship,

218
00:12:51,465 --> 00:12:52,785
for work.

219
00:12:52,865 --> 00:12:54,545
It's not for dating.

220
00:12:55,425 --> 00:12:56,265
Besides,

221
00:12:57,505 --> 00:12:58,945
the person I'm interested in

222
00:12:59,025 --> 00:13:00,865
is older than you,

223
00:13:00,945 --> 00:13:03,545
but not older than Dad.

224
00:13:03,625 --> 00:13:05,865
Don't be so petty.

225
00:13:05,945 --> 00:13:08,705
Just because you didn't date in college

226
00:13:08,785 --> 00:13:10,185
and can't find a girlfriend now,

227
00:13:10,265 --> 00:13:11,505
you can't be jealous of me.

228
00:13:11,585 --> 00:13:13,665
You need to be more magnanimous.

229
00:13:16,145 --> 00:13:17,425
Don't get it wrong.

230
00:13:17,505 --> 00:13:19,145
I'm not jealous at all.

231
00:13:19,225 --> 00:13:22,785
I have a girlfriend.

232
00:13:26,025 --> 00:13:27,185
Also, let me tell you.

233
00:13:27,265 --> 00:13:29,465
Don't become stupid after falling in love.

234
00:13:29,545 --> 00:13:31,505
When you met your online friend
during high school,

235
00:13:31,585 --> 00:13:33,105
you were only young and rebellious.

236
00:13:34,545 --> 00:13:35,985
You have to come home for the summer.

237
00:13:36,065 --> 00:13:36,905
Listen.

238
00:13:37,825 --> 00:13:39,825
I dare you to not come back.

239
00:13:39,905 --> 00:13:42,065
I'll fly there and drag you home myself.

240
00:13:48,385 --> 00:13:49,225
Who…

241
00:13:50,425 --> 00:13:52,785
Who would believe
that you have a girlfriend?

242
00:13:53,505 --> 00:13:54,785
You are just lying to me.

243
00:13:55,545 --> 00:13:56,825
And besides…

244
00:13:57,345 --> 00:13:59,225
Besides, I am staying

245
00:13:59,705 --> 00:14:01,665
to work at an internship.

246
00:14:01,745 --> 00:14:03,225
If you don't agree,

247
00:14:03,305 --> 00:14:04,905
I will tell Mom.

248
00:14:07,425 --> 00:14:08,745
You are so irritating!

249
00:14:13,105 --> 00:14:14,705
Why didn't you invite Chen Qiang?

250
00:14:15,305 --> 00:14:16,905
The professor told him to go

251
00:14:16,985 --> 00:14:18,465
and retake the test.

252
00:14:19,385 --> 00:14:21,625
-Let's have dumplings again later.
-Noodles.

253
00:14:21,705 --> 00:14:23,305
-Dumplings!
-Let's have noodles again.

254
00:14:23,385 --> 00:14:24,665
-Just once.
-It's really good.

255
00:14:24,745 --> 00:14:25,945
Give me a minute.

256
00:14:26,025 --> 00:14:27,025
Just a minute.

257
00:14:28,145 --> 00:14:29,145
Where are you going?

258
00:14:29,225 --> 00:14:30,065
What are you doing?

259
00:14:36,585 --> 00:14:37,505
Jiang Ming.

260
00:14:38,065 --> 00:14:38,905
Hi, Wangwang.

261
00:14:40,025 --> 00:14:41,185
This is for you.

262
00:14:41,265 --> 00:14:42,785
My mom said this works well

263
00:14:42,865 --> 00:14:44,065
for bruises and sprains.

264
00:14:45,785 --> 00:14:46,625
Thank you.

265
00:14:47,265 --> 00:14:49,225
What is going on?

266
00:14:50,865 --> 00:14:53,585
-At the basketball court yesterday,
-What is she doing?

267
00:14:53,665 --> 00:14:55,305
you asked about Sangsang's brother.

268
00:14:56,425 --> 00:14:57,345
It's okay.

269
00:14:57,825 --> 00:14:59,385
Sang Zhi has found someone she likes.

270
00:14:59,465 --> 00:15:00,505
I should be happy for her.

271
00:15:02,065 --> 00:15:03,745
-Sang Zhi?
-I'm glad you're okay.

272
00:15:05,105 --> 00:15:06,625
They are talking and smiling.

273
00:15:08,345 --> 00:15:09,745
Thank you for the ointment.

274
00:15:09,825 --> 00:15:11,985
I'll return it when I'm done with it.

275
00:15:12,065 --> 00:15:13,065
It's okay.

276
00:15:13,145 --> 00:15:14,345
I'm leaving now.

277
00:15:14,425 --> 00:15:15,305
Okay.

278
00:15:16,145 --> 00:15:17,625
-Bye.
-Bye.

279
00:15:20,305 --> 00:15:21,665
-What was that?
-What's going on?

280
00:15:21,745 --> 00:15:23,145
-What's up?
-What's the situation?

