566
00:35:54,825 --> 00:35:56,825
I'll always be by your side.

567
00:36:11,385 --> 00:36:12,745
By the way,

568
00:36:13,905 --> 00:36:15,625
there are some things

569
00:36:15,705 --> 00:36:17,425
I feel I should let you know.

570
00:36:19,705 --> 00:36:21,505
I don't think I've told you

571
00:36:22,065 --> 00:36:23,905
about my family situation.

572
00:36:24,785 --> 00:36:25,985
The thing is,

573
00:36:26,785 --> 00:36:28,825
my mom has passed away.

574
00:36:29,865 --> 00:36:30,945
And my dad

575
00:36:31,545 --> 00:36:32,545
is in a coma.

576
00:36:33,545 --> 00:36:35,905
He killed someone while drunk driving.

577
00:36:36,745 --> 00:36:38,825
But I've paid off the compensation.

578
00:36:40,585 --> 00:36:41,745
Right now,

579
00:36:42,545 --> 00:36:43,545
I don't

580
00:36:44,105 --> 00:36:45,185
own a house,

581
00:36:45,265 --> 00:36:46,545
but I have a car.

582
00:36:46,625 --> 00:36:48,105
I also have some savings.

583
00:36:54,105 --> 00:36:55,145
I'm sorry

584
00:36:56,945 --> 00:36:58,985
to bring this up out of the blue.

585
00:37:00,065 --> 00:37:01,305
Please don't feel uncomfortable.

586
00:37:01,385 --> 00:37:03,465
I'm not uncomfortable.

587
00:37:04,665 --> 00:37:07,105
I'm just worried
that talking about these things

588
00:37:08,705 --> 00:37:10,145
might make you sad.

589
00:37:11,865 --> 00:37:13,385
Why would I feel sad?

590
00:37:16,505 --> 00:37:17,785
But

591
00:37:19,745 --> 00:37:22,025
I admit that I might be a bit nervous.

592
00:37:24,785 --> 00:37:25,905
Why?

593
00:37:31,985 --> 00:37:33,905
I'm worried that you will mind.

594
00:37:36,665 --> 00:37:38,025
I don't mind.

595
00:38:11,785 --> 00:38:13,665
Sang Zhi, is there a power outage?

596
00:38:13,745 --> 00:38:14,865
I think so.

597
00:38:14,945 --> 00:38:15,785
Okay.

598
00:38:19,705 --> 00:38:20,545
Hello.

599
00:38:20,625 --> 00:38:23,065
Girlfriend, are you free later?

600
00:38:23,145 --> 00:38:24,225
Let's have lunch together.

601
00:38:25,185 --> 00:38:27,025
I'm going to the library to study.

602
00:38:27,105 --> 00:38:28,545
How about another day?

603
00:38:28,625 --> 00:38:29,785
The library?

604
00:38:30,425 --> 00:38:31,505
Can't you keep me company?

605
00:38:32,265 --> 00:38:33,145
Another day.

606
00:38:33,225 --> 00:38:34,145
All right then.

607
00:38:34,225 --> 00:38:35,225
Bye.

608
00:38:50,665 --> 00:38:51,785
What are you doing here?

609
00:38:52,385 --> 00:38:54,145
The power is out.
There's nowhere to study.

610
00:38:54,225 --> 00:38:55,305
Why didn't you tell me?

611
00:38:56,185 --> 00:38:58,145
I was just about to go to the library.

612
00:38:58,225 --> 00:38:59,825
I know which library you mean.

613
00:38:59,905 --> 00:39:01,345
It's the one nearby.

614
00:39:01,425 --> 00:39:02,625
There is very limited seating.

615
00:39:02,705 --> 00:39:04,545
All seats will have been taken by now.

616
00:39:05,785 --> 00:39:06,705
Then…

617
00:39:07,825 --> 00:39:09,945
-There is a café up ahead.
-Come to my place.

618
00:39:12,105 --> 00:39:13,185
Your place?

619
00:39:14,865 --> 00:39:15,825
To study.

620
00:39:21,185 --> 00:39:22,545
You haven't eaten, right?

621
00:39:22,625 --> 00:39:23,545
Perfect.

622
00:39:23,625 --> 00:39:25,265
I'll make something tasty for you later.

623
00:39:25,345 --> 00:39:26,665
You can cook too?

624
00:39:28,065 --> 00:39:29,345
I have a lot of skills.

625
00:39:30,025 --> 00:39:30,945
Such as?

626
00:39:32,105 --> 00:39:33,305
Such as…

627
00:39:51,385 --> 00:39:52,665
Change into slippers.

628
00:39:56,705 --> 00:39:58,745
You can study in my room later.

629
00:39:59,505 --> 00:40:00,585
There's a desk inside.

630
00:40:02,465 --> 00:40:03,345
I…

631
00:40:04,145 --> 00:40:07,665
I can just study here.

632
00:40:07,745 --> 00:40:09,665
I don't need to go to your room.

633
00:40:09,745 --> 00:40:11,705
I'll be cooking here later.

634
00:40:11,785 --> 00:40:13,505
Won't I disturb your studying?

635
00:40:17,385 --> 00:40:18,545
What are you thinking?

636
00:40:23,385 --> 00:40:25,225
I've already tidied up the desk for you.

637
00:40:30,305 --> 00:40:31,985
Study well.

638
00:40:32,825 --> 00:40:36,665
Jiaxu, what will you be doing

639
00:40:36,745 --> 00:40:37,825
while I study?

640
00:40:39,145 --> 00:40:40,225
I will

641
00:40:40,305 --> 00:40:41,505
just be sitting here.

642
00:40:43,665 --> 00:40:44,825
You'll just be sitting here?

643
00:40:45,465 --> 00:40:47,905
I want to look at you more.

644
00:41:19,225 --> 00:41:23,985
LUOKA BAKING

645
00:41:24,065 --> 00:41:25,145
Welcome.

646
00:41:25,225 --> 00:41:26,865
-Hi.
-Hi.

647
00:41:26,945 --> 00:41:28,225
Excuse me.

648
00:41:28,305 --> 00:41:29,865
Do you make personalized cakes?

649
00:41:29,945 --> 00:41:31,185
Yes, we do.

650
00:41:31,905 --> 00:41:33,065
I have a picture.

651
00:41:33,825 --> 00:41:35,185
Can you make something like this?

652
00:41:35,825 --> 00:41:36,665
Yes, we can.

653
00:41:36,745 --> 00:41:38,505
When would you like to have it?

654
00:41:39,025 --> 00:41:40,465
Is next Monday okay?

655
00:41:41,345 --> 00:41:42,945
Yes. Let me take it down.

656
00:41:48,905 --> 00:41:50,105
Miss, what is your surname?

657
00:41:50,185 --> 00:41:51,025
Sang.

658
00:41:54,945 --> 00:41:56,625
An eight-inch cake.

659
00:41:56,705 --> 00:41:57,825
Miss, your phone is ringing.

660
00:41:58,385 --> 00:41:59,785
Have you taken a photo?

661
00:41:59,865 --> 00:42:01,185
Yes. Go ahead.

662
00:42:04,065 --> 00:42:04,985
Hello, Mom.

663
00:42:05,065 --> 00:42:06,225
Hi, Zhizhi.

664
00:42:07,505 --> 00:42:09,105
I was outside just now.

665
00:42:09,185 --> 00:42:10,465
I just got home.

666
00:42:10,545 --> 00:42:13,705
Did you say something
about the recipe for longevity noodles?

667
00:42:13,785 --> 00:42:15,385
Is it someone's birthday?

668
00:42:16,185 --> 00:42:17,665
It's Jiaxu's birthday.

669
00:42:18,705 --> 00:42:19,825
So it's Xiaoduan.

670
00:42:21,825 --> 00:42:24,465
I'm studying in Yihe

671
00:42:24,545 --> 00:42:27,025
and Jiaxu has been taking care of me.

672
00:42:27,785 --> 00:42:29,545
He's all alone here.

673
00:42:29,625 --> 00:42:32,145
So I thought

674
00:42:32,665 --> 00:42:35,745
I would make longevity noodles for him.

675
00:42:35,825 --> 00:42:36,745
But

676
00:42:36,825 --> 00:42:39,345
I'm sure you make the most delicious one.

677
00:42:40,785 --> 00:42:42,705
You're becoming more considerate.

678
00:42:43,905 --> 00:42:46,305
Okay, I'll write out the recipe
for longevity noodles

679
00:42:46,385 --> 00:42:47,425
and send it to you later.

680
00:42:47,505 --> 00:42:48,665
Okay.

681
00:42:52,785 --> 00:42:53,625
Bye.

682
00:42:56,145 --> 00:42:57,625
Miss, take a look.

683
00:42:57,705 --> 00:42:59,225
It will be an eight-inch cake

684
00:42:59,305 --> 00:43:00,705
to be picked up next Monday.

685
00:43:00,785 --> 00:43:02,145
Will you be picking it up yourself?

686
00:43:02,225 --> 00:43:03,545
-Yes.
-Okay.

687
00:43:03,625 --> 00:43:05,025
It's all set.

688
00:43:05,105 --> 00:43:05,945
Thank you.
